<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>Brave prove is a japanese action RPG in which you take the role of Ars, a warrior member of a legendary band of thieves that with the help of Shina (a young girl) will try to defeat the evil Chaos that is in his land. The game starts when Shina goes to the temple that is on the caves of the mountain that are to the right of the town where they live (that's the big first level of the game).
                  <br><br>When the player arrives at the temple in the bottom of the mountain he finds Shina praying to the rock of the 2 elements, but soon a fire demon appears and to defeat it the player has to destroy the rock. When he do that a demon appears and stole Shina powers after that a fairy appears and they return to the town to cure Shina. After that they adventure to defeat the devil demon has just started.
                  <br><br>In the game the player can use Elementals that can do two things: First they allow the player to use magic and second they give the player's sword special properties.
                  <br><br>The gameplay is pure action (like in Alundra or The Legend of Thor) since the player have to defeat the enemies with his sword or with special attacks or items (like bombs), in some parts of the game to advance he will have to use bombs to break through walls or other things in his way.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Numerous actions to trigger a combo thing after another in real time command input actions to continuously pay out several simple commands. Hit attack combo is determined refreshing sense of fun. Technical skill and technique of attack together from flashy special attacks and invigoration of the charm of that unique skill to instantly annihilate the enemy are endless. Action-oriented action patterns alone provides 400 patterns of the hero RPG.
                  <br><br>As drew a full-scale action adventure black member of the legendary band of thieves looking RPG on PS crystals appeared. Continue to exercise after another in real time by typing several actions to continuously go out with a simple command "action combo"adopted. Excellent taste a sense of exhilaration in the attack pattern of an infinite combination of flashy super special technique to annihilate the enemy at once.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>2D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Medieval Fantasy theme.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

